TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Use to extract the data from source tables

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT F.dData dollars , EY.Label year, ED.Label period, EP.Label sbu, EA2.Label measure, ES.LABEL scenario from dbo.PBACTPEG_FACT F with (nolock) join dbo.PBACTPEG_ENTITY EC with (nolock) on F.EntityID=EC.id join dbo.PBACTPEG_ENTITY_PARENT EX with (nolock) on EX.ChildID=EC.id join dbo.PBACTPEG_ENTITY EP with (nolock) on EP.id=EX.ParentID join dbo.PBACTPEG_ACCOUNT EA with (nolock) on EA.ID=F.AccountID join dbo.PBACTPEG_ACCOUNT_PARENT EA1 with (nolock) on EA.ID=EA1.ChildID join dbo.PBACTPEG_ACCOUNT EA2 with (nolock) on EA1.ParentID=EA2.ID join dbo.PBACTPEG_PERIOD ED with (nolock) on ED.ID=F.PeriodID join dbo.PBACTPEG_SCENARIO ES with (nolock) on ES.ID=f.ScenarioID join dbo.PBACTPEG_YEAR EY with (nolock) on EY.ID=F.YearID where EY.label = $$FISCAL_YEAR order by ED.Label, EP.Label, EA.Label, ES.LABEL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select p.strategic_business_unit sbu, g.fiscal_year year,g.fiscal_period period, g.cost_measure_name measure, g.adj_ext_cst_dol_local_currency from slba.gross_margin g join slba.edm_profit_center p on g.sap_profit_center_num=p.profit_center where g.slba_division_code='HA' and gross_margin_ind='Y' and g.fiscal_year =$$FISCAL_YEAR and g.fiscal_period in ($$FISCAL_PERIOD) order by g.cost_measure_name
